                    coach hinds in the past and he is a very cool person</p>

                <br>

                <h5><b>What other hobbies do you enjoy?</b></h5>
                <p>I like gaming and usually that’s about all I do.</p>

                <br>

                <h5><b>Favorite memory about Esports so far?</b></h5>
                <p>It was really fun to play my first valorant game the experience was just really fun. </p>

                <br>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
